    <uniqueid>false</uniqueid>
    <dtdversion>3.0</dtdversion>

  <operation>
    <authentication>
      <sessionid>{{temp_session_id}}</sessionid>
    </authentication>
    <content>
      <function controlid="{{$guid}}">
        <readByQuery>
          <object>ACTIVITYLOG</object>
          <fields>*</fields>
          <query>OBJ_ID > 10000 AND CREATED_AT >= '04/19/2012 12:00:00' AND CREATED_AT < '04/20/2012 12:00:00'</query>
          <pagesize>100</pagesize>
        </readByQuery>
      </function>
    </content>
  </operation>
</request>
